<para style="q1">

<verse number="13" style="v" />Have mercy on me, Yahweh; see how I am oppressed by those who hate me,</para>

<para style="q1">you who can snatch me from the gates of death.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="14" style="v" />Oh, that I might proclaim all your praise.</para>

<para style="q1">In the gates of the daughter of Zion</para>

<para style="q1">I will rejoice in your salvation!</para>
